Class Execution

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.indra.iquality.model.Execution

  • public class Execution
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class Ejecucion. Represents an execution of an ETL flow for a given system and software version on a date. See Flow.
    Version:
    0.1, 09/12/15 The Class Ejecucion.
    Author:
    Ignacio N. Lucero Ascencio
